# Our Workspace Framework

`packages/ui/src/components/compose/workspace/` is **human-owned**. Not a sandbox for agent polish passes.

## Stupid behaviors to avoid here

- Editing shell/sidebar/memory-lane/surfaces/typography to "fix" Theme Studio or Storybook look
- Changing defaults (`sidebarVariant`, tokens, orbit layout) because a preview looked wrong
- Running `git restore` / `git clean` on this folder or related WIP without explicit instruction

## Where visual work belongs instead

| Goal | Edit here |
|------|-----------|
| Theme Studio preview layout | `apps/app/app/theme-studio/` |
| App shell wiring | `apps/app/app/_components/workspace/` |
| Storybook demos | `apps/storybook/` |
| Entity/metadata screens | App routes + `@repo/metadata-ui` |

## If blocked on a framework bug

Stop and ask: *"This needs a change in `@repo/ui` workspace compose. Approve edit to `<file>`?"*

Do not "helpfully" patch the framework and apologize later.
